text: Göran Breisner (born 1 July 1954) is a Swedish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Malmö
